        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This vial of glowing goo constantly sheds dim light in a 10-foot radius. When a bioluminescence bomb strikes a creature or a hard surface, it shatters and releases the bioluminescent fluid's energy in a flare of light. Each creature within @Template[type:burst|distance:10]{10 feet} of where the bomb exploded must succeed at a @Check[type:reflex|dc:17] or be marked with dye that continues to glow for 24 hours. An affected creature must also attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:17] saving throw against the overwhelming burst of light.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] for 1 round, then dazzled for 1 round.</p>"
